CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1962, pg. 17 reads: "Y's Men Meet - The tenth anniversary committee of the Centre Avenue Y's Men completes plans for the group's celebration, which will be held Oct. 20 at 6:30 P.M. at the YMCA. Left to right, seated: Lawrence Cosby, secretary; Frank Lavelle, president; Robert Jinks, past president, and Andrew Frazier, vice president.  Standing: Dr. Neal Smith, program chairman; Paul Dykes of the 'Y' staff, Atty. David Hill and James Burgette, executive secretary of the 'Y.' - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Centre Avenue YMCA Mens committee, seated from left: Lawrence Cosby, Frank Lavelle, Robert Jinks, Andrew Frazier; standing: Dr. Neal Smith, Paul Dykes, Atty. David Hill, and James Burgette, gathered at table in Greene Hearth
